Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:52.82,ed.jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be10}舞い上がる風に乗り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:57.90,ed.jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be10}歌え　LIVE　LIVE　LIVE
